reviewText:
As the title says, this is a must have for any 2NE1 fan!

As 2NE1 are no more, you can relive them at their best over-and-over.
Love it only wish I could've been there in person

This is an amazing DVD :D I'm a huge fan of the band so finding this under my Christmas tree was the best thing that could have happen to me! I was SUPER worried that because it has Region 3 Encoding that it wouldn't play. As soon as I pressed play on my DVD player it started up without a problem :) I was so relieved and happy! This is the perfect gift for any fan of 2NE1 ;D

This is one awesome DVD. It's an unbelievable set. With a great book and just a great overall DVD package. The content is high quality and if you're a fan it's the best content they have out. Awesome!

BIG 2NE1 FAN LOVE THIS DVD AND WOULD DEFIANTLY SAY ITS A MUST BUY IF YOU REALLY LIKE THIS GROUP. I ONLY WISH THAT WHEN THEY WHERE HERE IN THE U.S. THAT THERE CONCERT WAS THE SAME AS THE DVD BUT, IF I WAS THEM I WOULDN'T TRUST THE U.S. CROWD AND WALK THROUGH THEM.

After the worry of "I hope this plays" wore off and I actually got the DVD, I was very happy with it. Everything was there and nothing was scratched or bent or messed up at all. I got it earlier than expected and I love it. Totally recommend it for a fan of this group. I would buy from this source again though.

It was my first purchase on Amazon, I wanted a DVD of my favorite band, 2NE1. I tried on many shopping sites, but none gave me what I really wanted, only to Amazon. I found several vendors here and a great guarantee of delivery. My business is going well and soon my product will be in my hands. Blackjacks from around the world, I recommend buying.
